description: This 20-minute beef stir-fry is perfect for a weeknight meal. It's quick, tasty and colourful thanks to the addition of broccolini, carrot and capsicum.
name: Steak & Veg Stir Fry Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 2 tbs kecap manus sweet soy sauce

recipeInstructions.text: Return beef to the pan, add oyster sauce and kecap manus sweet soy sauce, and toss to coat. Serve stir fry over steamed rice, with spring onions and lemon wedges.
